data.description: Nice, neat and private! Split plan two bedrooms two baths. Florida room added for your enjoyment. Patio to enjoy Florida morning and evenings. Kitchen has new granite counter tops as well as both bathrooms.  Kitchen island and pantry and new sink. New roof in last couple years. Extra large driveway. Shelving in garage and attic space for storage. Gutters in front and rear. AC serviced and good condition. Laminate flooring in both bedrooms and neutral tile everywhere else. Come see this little blue gem! Washer dryer negotiable.
